---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import articlesData from './Data/procesos_academicos.json';
import Topic from "./Topic.astro";
---
<Container>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center mt-16" id="procesos-academicos">
    <Topic title="Procesos Académicos" description="Descubre los diferentes procesos académicos que ofrecemos para mejorar tu experiencia educativa." />
  </div>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center my-4 w-full">
      <div class="flex-grow border-t border-red-300"></div>
      <span class="mx-4 text-red-300">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <div class="flex-grow border-t border-red-300"></div>
    </div>
    Explora nuestros procesos académicos diseñados para ayudarte a alcanzar tus metas educativas con eficacia y apoyo continuo.
  </div>
  <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      {articlesData.map(({ id, title, description }) => (
        <article class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">{title}</h2>
          <p class="mb-5 text-gray-600">{description}</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-4">
            <a href={`/proceso_academico/${id}`} class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-black hover:text-red-600">
              Leer más
              <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>  
  </div>
</Container>
